Sequencer
	Contains 12 rows (1 octave)
	Rows (Notes) contain amplitudes corresponding to points in time (certain beats, durations)
	Each note has an Oscillator
	Attack and decay?
	
Controllers change sequencer parameters
Uses JACK audio to output sound
	on each buffer get, the sequencer adds up notes and their amplitudes according to time intervals


